data.description: Don't miss this beautiful home that offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this spacious home is ideal for those who appreciate ample living space. Step inside and be greeted by the inviting dining room, featuring laminate flooring that adds a touch of elegance. The island kitchen is complete with granite counters, gas cooking, an above-the-range microwave, and a walk-in pantry. The adjacent breakfast area provides a cozy spot for casual dining. The interior of this home has been freshly painted and showcases updated fixtures, doorknobs, and lighting throughout, creating a modern and cohesive aesthetic. Downstairs, you'll find gorgeous tile flooring laid in an offset pattern, adding a unique touch of sophistication to the living spaces. Upstairs, discover a spacious loft that offers versatility for various needs, whether it be a play area, home office, or entertainment space. All bedrooms are conveniently located on this level, providing privacy and comfort for all family members. The primary suite offers a generous amount of space and an ensuite bath that features dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a standing shower. Outside, a large backyard awaits, ready to be transformed into your own personal retreat or an outdoor entertainment area for hosting friends and family. Additional features of this home include a water softener, ensuring quality water throughout, and the convenience of being just minutes away from the popular Alamo Ranch shopping center, offering a wide array of retail and dining options.
